creator: Cowbeans
descriptionHtml:
You have been summoned, Hero!

Because you have the skills, we need you to defeat the monsters in Pixel Survival!
Because you have the desire to craft, we need you to craft the ultimate items!
Because you have the need to explore, we want you to explore and find all the treasures!
Because you want to be the richest, you will trade with other players and become the richest!

FEATUERS
- Online multiplayer with other players around the world
- Find monster eggs and hatch them into cool pets!
- over hundreds of items to discover
- craft mysterious items with secret combinations
- monster hunting
- survival games
- boss fights!
descriptionShort: Adventure, Fight, Loot, Harvest, Craft, Explore, Trade and More!

title: Pixel Survival Game 2.o

creator: Cowbeans
descriptionHtml:
You have been summoned, Hero!

Gather materials and discover combination secrets to complete quests at Silly Npc. Acquire new equipments through crafting and looting monsters to adventure and survive into more difficult areas.

Unlock the Bounty board to do daily missions for awesome prizes!

Use Special Keys and Magical Seeds to gain special equipment quickly. Craft equipments and items at Town blacksmiths.

Have loose unwanted items? Sell them for coins to the local npc or trade them away to fellow players with VIP access!

There are lots awaiting you in Pixel Survival Game 2.o!
